    <body>
        
        <div type="letter">
            <div type="text">
                <opener>
                    <placeName><hi rend="print">Down, | Beckenham, Kent.</hi></placeName>
                    <date>July 13</date>
                    <salute>My dear M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Murray</salute>
                </opener>
                <div type="transcription">
                     
<p>Many thanks for your kind present of the Q. Review. I have read only a few pages; but I see it is a cutting article, &amp; apparently worthy of M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>. Mivart’s skill.<ref target="#foot.f2"/></p>
<p>Yours sincerely | Ch. Darwin</p> 
                </div>
            </div>

            
            
            
        </div>

        

        

        <div type="footnotes">
            <note xml:id="foot.f1">The year is established by the reference to <ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_3350.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">St George Jackson Mivart’s</ref> anonymous review of <ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_1966.xml" resp="#mjhawkins"><hi rend="italic">Descent</hi></ref> (see n. 2, below).</note>
            <note xml:id="foot.f2">Mivart’s review of <ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_1966.xml" resp="#mjhawkins"><hi rend="italic">Descent</hi></ref> was published in the <hi rend="italic">Quarterly Review</hi> for July 1871 ([Mivart] 1871c). Murray was the publisher of the <hi rend="italic">Quarterly Review.</hi></note>
        </div>        
            
